name: General Rules
content:
2. Use common sense.
  3. If you find yourself using a "loophole" in the rules to your advantage, it is likely you are breaking at least one other rule.

  5. No politics, harassment, sexism, racism, discrimination, bigotry, porn, NSFW content, malicious behavior, etc.

  7. Crossfire is counted as RDM.

  9. Running into spawn to avoid any roleplay situation is considered FailRP.

  11. No class can /advert murder or /advert counter.
  12. No propspam, propminge, propsurf, propclimb, propblock, bodyblock etc.


  1. Do not FailRP and/or FearRP.
  2. *FearRP is doing something roleplay wise out of fear. (e.g. someone is pointing a gun at you, you are not allowed to take out a weapon or run away). *FailRP is doing something against the rules or your job rules/description.
  3. Voice-changers aren't allowed.

  5. No mass RPbinds, all binds must specify one action, you cannot bind test too.



Now Master
